」<br />\n但轉頭返到屋企好凍就開恒個暖氣啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T00:36:23.000Z","msg":"搞錯左，係屋企冇熄過暖氣等佢返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffb0b595fd63efba82cf23882748b953dd300ee6","tid":2361414,"uid":70724,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"02f48b2f5cbe799ede21de1ff674131a28f0a249","tid":2361414,"uid":21141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T15:42:27.000Z","msg":"好多裝置藝術都睇唔出藝術成份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T00:40:23.000Z","msg":"Netflix套抽象的藝術第二集就係講呢個artist<br />\n有興趣可以上去睇下 應該會令你改觀<br />\n小弟有幸睇過一次佢嘅個展 係真係會令人哇哇聲"},{"pid":"3d94c2549f8d34818d20ab7a40899ffc67342c5a","tid":2361414,"uid":116967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T02:38:53.000Z","msg":"如果可以用番當地嘅冰整會比較欣賞<br />\n始終北極唔夠冰<br />\n佢背後幾有意義都好都覺得唔應該拎北極冰"},{"pid":"071a57ea7fec2638fde3f87627819d9f7a450738","tid":2361414,"uid":220089,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3d94c2549f8d34818d20ab7a40899ffc67342c5a","tid":2361414,"uid":116967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T02:38:53.000Z","msg":"如果可以用番當地嘅冰整會比較欣賞<br />\n始終北極唔夠冰<br />\n佢背後幾有意義都好都覺得唔應該拎北極冰"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T02:46:59.000Z","msg":"其實呢類浮冰係冰川或者巨型浮冰自然脫落嘅碎冰嚟，一星期內就會溶咗喺海入邊，而且當地動物都用唔着呢類浮冰。所以其實影響唔係好大。<br />\n<br />\n啲人成日話北極唔夠冰，係講緊冰川因為氣候問題冇落雪，冰川先會縮細，同埋海冰溶得太快，影響北極熊覓食。"},{"pid":"1b0a2837631b3ee4b6dd30c5fb3e700195425588","tid":2361414,"uid":28019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T03:51:56.000Z","msg":"見佢成日講大自然，件件都好有power咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n太陽嗰份好想親身感受下..<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2m5fRyA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2m5fRyA.jpg&h=66e47206&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a0e3ccefa7d8038cf27a6928449e3eec9b19b78c","tid":2361414,"uid":2